The paper proposes a new prior model for image denoising using group sparsity, which is a common technique in computer vision and image processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves optimization and signal processing techniques, which are related to cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.MM (Multimedia). The proposed method also involves machine learning concepts such as regularization and feature selection, which are related to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
